        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1636019491" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10436006585963891563">I really enjoyed this book. Which is surprising, because I&apos;m not usually into historical romances. I&apos;m also not very knowledgeable about van Gogh, but I thought the story was beautiful. Rachel&apos;s motives were a bit off for me, but I don&apos;t hold it against the overall story. I would definitely recommend looking at the paintings while reading. It greatly enhanced my experience.</span>
  <span id="freeText10436006585963891563" style="display:none">I really enjoyed this book. Which is surprising, because I'm not usually into historical romances. I'm also not very knowledgeable about van Gogh, but I thought the story was beautiful. Rachel's motives were a bit off for me, but I don't hold it against the overall story. I would definitely recommend looking at the paintings while reading. It greatly enhanced my experience.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10436006585963891563" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
